I tried again this morning.

Reset the LimeLight to DHCP mode. Was able to connect through limelight.local.5801.

Set team number static ip to 10.22.52.11 mask to 255.255.255.0 and gateway to 10.22.52.1 hit update and power cycled.

The orange light on the LL goes to solid showing it is in static ip mode, but I am unable to connect to it with either limelight.local:5801 or by entering ip address while connected to limelight with ethernet cable run to the camera.

I have reflashed the firmware and rebooted computer and tried a different laptop.
